<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #333;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .content {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 50px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="title">SELF DECLARATION OF INCOME</div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>This is to certify that I, <strong>{{fullName}}</strong>, am the head of the family residing at
            <strong>{{address}}</strong>.</p>

        <p>I hereby declare that my annual family income from all sources including salary/business/agriculture for the
            financial year ending March {{year}} is <strong>{{annualIncome}}</strong>.</p>

        <p>I understand that if this information is found to be incorrect, my scholarship application will be rejected
            and legal action may be taken.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>Date: {{date}}</p>
        <p>Place: _______________</p>
        <br><br>
        <p>__________________________</p>
        <p>Signature of Parent/Guardian</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>